ated Catholics]]\n[[Category:Businesspeople from Scranton, Pennsylvania]]\n[[Category:Catholic Mariology]]\n[[Category:Catholic television]]\n[[Category:Congregation of Holy Cross]]\n[[Category:Evangelists]]\n[[Category:Irish anti-communists]]\n[[Category:Irish Roman Catholic priests]]\n[[Category:Irish emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:Irish film producers]]\n[[Category:Irish radio producers]]\n[[Category:Irish television producers]]\n[[Category:Religious leaders from County Mayo]]\n[[Category:Roman Catholic writers]]\n[[Category:Servants of God]]\n[[Category:Television evangelists]]\n[[Category:University of Notre Dame people]]\n[[Category:Venerated Catholics by Pope Francis]]\n[[Category:20th-century Roman Catholic priests]]\n[[Category:20th-century Irish clergy]]\n", "name_user": "Jzsj", "label": "safe", "comment": "mf", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Peyton"}
